  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5353163/" class="title-link">《洗脑术》里捡的乐子</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5353163"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/w.slash/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u36737038-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/w.slash/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">.</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-03-20"
      class="main-meta">2012-03-20 10:30:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5353163_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《洗脑术》里捡的乐子。说二战时候战略情报局找来一个叫洛弗尔的专门做药。有回他做了种致命的胶丸，本来要分发给妓女对付日本军官，但后来没用上，因为负责运输的官员决定在船上测试，给一头驴吃了两颗，发现没效果后就把剩下的抛进了海里。洛弗尔气疯了，因为世上唯一对这种...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5353163/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
